title: IFaxServer::get_DiscountRateEndHour (faxcom.h)
description: Sets or retrieves the DiscountRateEndHour property for a FaxServer object. The DiscountRateEndHour property is a number that represents the hour the discount period ends. The discount period applies only to outgoing fax transmissions. (Get)
